<subSubSection id="580925C43F9796119CC81E8B7D2ADE1E" pageId="null" pageNumber="532" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph id="FD2241C9EF742CB1573B9157DE9195E7" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">
<taxonomicName id="DA0FEE6DE2774F4E558D14683B65D14C" authority="Waldst. et Kit." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Solidago" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="532" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="alpestris">
Solidago 
<normalizedToken id="39C963E7C8DBD063372B2C1D3E2A4FF2" originalValue="alpéstris" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">alpestris</normalizedToken>
Waldst. et Kit.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="FE247AD1900F932C6A9EB6071FABF085" pageId="null" pageNumber="532" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="1172F70B09034C38BB5F4B8CF7CE07D4" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Alpen-Goldrute</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="9D37492F91CA9352C6D748B18B26107F" pageId="null" pageNumber="532" type="description">
<paragraph id="3DEED137D596F72BE50B49BD9DC4B8B2" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<emphasis id="BEFD9F3A5B3F9F7D58D2C8B68D32B3CC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">S. Virga-aurea</emphasis>
(Nr. 4) durch folgende Merkmale: 6-40 cm hoch; 
<normalizedToken id="6545A965A7D12EA08A8CE20594A7DE01" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="71F670842FDFFFABA7AE2DBAA7D5304C" originalValue="schmäler" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">schmaeler</normalizedToken>
, 
<emphasis id="529516D12F9192B540AC093541E6BB38" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">4</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="E65CFED6C6ACF4CB6608A330DF8A5F68" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">6mal so lang wie breit</emphasis>
(mit Stiel); 
<emphasis id="5C5D22996300359954949A7F1C1E42D0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">
<normalizedToken id="71117562991088F9F82B05EB93611214" originalValue="Blütenköpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Bluetenkoepfe</normalizedToken>
im Durchmesser 15
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="3D44CCC807CD86DB6B744A04BA39F583" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">
20 mm; 
<normalizedToken id="5B7BFFE2C9C0182F227037DEDA6EC18F" originalValue="Hülle" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Huelle</normalizedToken>
7
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="E44F25C342FE03CE9CE28DFF3E7452D1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">
10 mm lang; 
<normalizedToken id="A5551E97D0B8BA8B54D81AFC639635E8" originalValue="Hüllblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Huellblaetter</normalizedToken>
lang und 
<normalizedToken id="018DDD19FC53F5E41CE56F95BA2CB3C9" originalValue="allmählich" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">allmaehlich</normalizedToken>
zugespitzt; 
<normalizedToken id="1D7538295947F90848D1443914A41B4D" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
4
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="543566BB223EC814CAC174506783A915" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">
6 mm lang; 
<taxonomicName id="7684AA71FF3175CCE639B7B6E5B9BF15" class="Insecta" family="Miridae" genus="Pappus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="532" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Pappus</taxonomicName>
ca. 5 mm lang.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="FF39178F1B70BC3D39671138D5D7354C" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3CACDB21D7E570ECA48F3F0CB6116D96" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">
<emphasis id="6951DA75F2F5099906A7588D66147C85" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="D13C0957F4C952BADD592AB8171A29B9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">18:</emphasis>
Material aus dem Berner Oberland (Rohner 1954), aus den Ostkarpaten (Chouksanova et al. 1968a).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6D715EA10BEEAD26960FD32DB3CEC22D" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">
<emphasis id="D136E10D4B93A49AC4BD8FB74ADBB757" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin und alpin, selten tiefer herabgeschwemmt. Steinige, meist kalkarme und saure, humose 
<normalizedToken id="E0BDE06469D2751C847EB69AC83CCE2B" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="8BE31172B1C02154FD505235F2B63155" originalValue="Zwergstrauchbestände" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Zwergstrauchbestaende</normalizedToken>
, Wiesen, Weiden, Hochstaudenfluren, 
<normalizedToken id="B2E8ED56DA4E1065696EE8A233FE1239" originalValue="Bachgeröll" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Bachgeroell</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6E456723D817C5EEFC1C8E722B7CA48A" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">
<emphasis id="2E10C4DE8DB62B19BAEE81AF6CB8288D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Verbreitung.</emphasis>
Siehe unter Bemerkungen bei 
<emphasis id="88922B4D73430C0BB1D030B913CF685F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">S. Virga-aurea</emphasis>
(Nr. 4). - Im Gebiet: Alpen, Jura, Vogesen, Schwarzwald; ziemlich 
<normalizedToken id="1B053629EB04E0FCE957BEB50B8784C0" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9292C8ABFE80B6CE2E2FCD8DF9E12E44" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">
<emphasis id="CF0B1C7BAC730F0107A993D0C9416FFA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Nach Turesson (1931a) ist unsere Art 
<normalizedToken id="13FDF775C55FDB3A32AD0AEAAD8200D3" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">+/-</normalizedToken>
identisch mit dem subalpinen 
<normalizedToken id="680DDAE891AC4CD495AB50765594A963" originalValue="Ökotyp" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">Oekotyp</normalizedToken>
in Skandinavien. Es ist 
<normalizedToken id="95C6F122219C0D22E9412BB4B382ABCB" originalValue="abzuklären" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">abzuklaeren</normalizedToken>
, ob sich der Name 
<taxonomicName id="BC4378763483976540B1065965ED43DB" authority="L." authorityName="L." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Solidago" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="532" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="minuta">
<emphasis id="015D6D1E1A05D99234698E48576745C4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">S. minuta</emphasis>
<authorityName id="C24E3D97CD4CF575B022A3E9993A99EB" pageId="null" pageNumber="532">L.</authorityName>
</taxonomicName>
auf unsere Art bezieht.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</treatment>
